g.text: K8Scluster›External Ingress ControllerWAF –API Security policy›Micro API GWRedirect browser to Okta for authenticationAuthenticate on login pageOkta sends redirect with authorization codeGET sentence-api.f5app.dev/_codexchfor code exchangeSends authorization code to Okta and receive ID tokenValidate ID token by downloading JWKCreate session cookieAPI GW sends redirect to original URIRequests original URI, supplying session cookieExtract JWT from cookie and local key-value store, validates signatureRate limit
